  <summary date="2021-03-02T19:41:31Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Alzheimer's Caregiver Support Act

This bill authorizes the Department of Health and Human Services to award grants to public and nonprofit private health care providers to expand training and support services for families and caregivers of individuals living with Alzheimer's disease or a related dementia.</summary>
